---
title: Italian Meatloaf with Green Beans and Garlicky Potatoes
description: Spiked with Italian flavors like sun-dried tomato and garlic, these mini meatloaves are what happens when an American classic spends a semester abroad in Rome. Their piccolo size doesn’t just make them adorable, it allows them to cook quickly, too. Even the mashed potatoes on the side, fragrant with rosemary and garlic, sneak in a little European flair.
